	   24. Kansas (19-7) beat No. 20 Oklahoma 53-50. Next: at Nebraska,
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
	   25. Purdue (19-7) did not play. Next: at Michigan, Thursday.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER> AP-NY-02-21-00 0139 </TRAILER>
