<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Charges Surface Against TV Groom  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    NEW YORK (AP) -- Fox canceled the rebroadcast of its highly rated special
"Who Wants to Marry a Multimillionaire?" after learning that the groom, Rick
Rockwell, once was accused of hitting and threatening to kill an ex-girlfriend.
</P>
<P>
