<HEADLINE> Gore, Bradley clash over racial profiling  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
    	   NEW YORK (AP) - In an angry Harlem debate, Al Gore accused Bill Bradley
of attack tactics that "divide us as Democrats," while the challenger described
